                Procula <expan><abbr>sp</abbr><ex>ectabilis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>emina</ex></expan> de don<supplied reason="lost">is</supplied><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <lb n="2"/>Dei et sanctorum recuperavi[t ------
